### Request Body:
```json
{
  "rows": [
    {
      "scheduleRowId": "15f97a53-85d0-4a09-91f6-a8d5050f64a7",
      "columns": [
        {
          "$type": "Metric",
          "columnName": "Revit Count",
          "metricData": [
            {
              "value": 50.50
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "$type": "Text",
          "columnName": "Revit Dimension (in)",
          "value": "45"
        },
        {
          "$type": "Bounded",
          "columnName": "Revit Material Name",
          "boundedData": [
            {
              "name": "Steel",
              "color": "FF5733"
            },
            {
              "name": "Rock",
              "color": "FF5733"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "scheduleRowId": "d51d4b5a-746c-4f86-9de1-0d67bded63e7",
      "columns": [
        {
          "$type": "Metric",
          "columnName": "Revit Count",
          "metricData": [
            {
              "value": 75.50
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "$type": "Text",
          "columnName": "Revit Dimension (in)",
          "value": "75"
        },
        {
          "$type": "Bounded",
          "columnName": "Revit Material Name",
          "boundedData": [
            {
              "name": "Rock",
              "color": "FF5733"
            },
            {
              "name": "Steel",
              "color": "FF5733"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```
**Field Descriptions:**
- `rows` (**array**, **required**) - List of rows to update.
- `scheduleRowId` (**GUID**, **required**) - Unique identifier for the schedule row.
- `columns` (**array**, **required**) - List of columns to update in the row.

**Column Types:**
- **Text Column**:
  - `$type` (**string**, **required**) - Must be "Text" for text columns.
  - `columnName` (**string**, **required**) - Name of the text column.
  - `value` (**string**, **required**) - Text value to set.
            
- **Metric Column**:
  - `$type` (**string**, **required**) - Must be "Metric" for metric columns.
  - `columnName` (**string**, **required**) - Name of the metric column.
  - `metricData` (**array**, **required**) - Array of metric values:
    - `value` (**decimal**, **required**) - Numeric value to set.
            
- **BoundedItem Column**:
  - `$type` (**string**, **required**) - Must be "Bounded" for bounded item columns.
  - `columnName` (**string**, **required**) - Name of the bounded item column.
  - `boundedData` (**array**, **required**) - Array of bounded items:
    - `name` (**string**, **required**) - Name of the bounded item.
    - `color` (**string**, **required**) - Color code for the bounded item (without # prefix).
            
### Response Example:
```json
{
  "successfulRowIds": [
    "15f97a53-85d0-4a09-91f6-a8d5050f64a7",
    "d51d4b5a-746c-4f86-9de1-0d67bded63e7"
  ],
  "failedRows": [
    {
      "scheduleRowId": "660e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440001",
      "failedColumns": [
        {
          "columnName": "Revit Material Name",
          "errorMessage": "Invalid bounded data format"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```
            
### Responses:
- **200 OK**: Updates processed successfully, returns results with successful and failed rows.
- **400 Bad Request**: Invalid input data or request format.
- **404 Not Found**: Project not found.
